T02TD2885E:227b-1: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2885E:227b-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba /
T02TD2885E:227b-3: klu rigs lnga la dug lnga ste //
T02TD2885E:227b-4: 'gro ba gzhan la gnod pa byed /
T02TD2885E:227b-5: gnod pa'i mtshan nyid 'di lta ste //
T02TD2885E:227b-6: brag par grog po gting rings dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-7: ri phug dog dang sgo dog mor //
T02TD2885E:227b-8: mi shong bzhin du 'tshang ba dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-9: lha khang khang phrul nyams mi dga' //
T02TD2885E:227b-10: chu dang 'dam rdzab zag pa ngan //
T02TD2885E:227b-11: g-yag dang ba glang ra lug dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-12: ri dgas gcan gzan khyi yis 'tshe //
T02TD2885E:227b-14: lus dang shes pa lci ba dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-15: gnyid che sems skyo snang glu len //
T02TD2885E:227b-16: spro thung snying mi dga' ba 'ong //
T02TD2885E:227b-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal ba //
T02TD2885E:227b-18: de dag bsrung dang gso bya'i phyir //
T02TD2885E:227b-19: rdzas kyi sbyor ba bstan par bya //
T02TD2885E:227b-20: thun mong sbyor ba bshad bya ba //
T02TD2885E:227b-21: ri dgas lte dri 'dre gsod chu //
T02TD2885E:227b-22: nags kyi rtsi dang rtsi bo che //
T02TD2885E:227b-23: dri chen nya yi mkhris pa dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-24: byi sku bdun du sbyar ba yis //
T02TD2885E:227b-25: klu gnyan sa bdag nag mod kor //
T02TD2885E:227b-26: 'byung po rnams kyis mi tshugs shing //
T02TD2885E:227b-27: mdze 'bras shu ba za kong dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-28: bas ldag g-yan pa med pa la dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-29: gag pa lhog pa rma rims dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-30: tshad rims rgyu gzer 'byung po'i nad //
T02TD2885E:227b-31: bza' dang gdags dang byugs dang bdugs //
T02TD2885E:227b-32: thams cad 'joms par byed pa'i mchog / khyad par sbyor ba rnam pa bzhi //
T02TD2885E:227b-33: lte dri shing kun aa ru ra //
T02TD2885E:227b-34: dri chus sbyangs shing khong du btung //
T02TD2885E:227b-35: skad snyan tshe ring nad skoms srung //
T02TD2885E:227b-36: lte dri 'dre gsod thang chu dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-37: nags kyi rtsi dang rtsi bo che //
T02TD2885E:227b-38: byi sku ha la dz'a ti dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-39: aa mri ta sbyar ba bcang ba'o //
T02TD2885E:227b-40: lte dri 'dre gsod ru rta nag / bdud rtsi rgya tshi las tshil dang //
T02TD2885E:227b-41: byi sku ha la mi phag bcud //
T02TD2885E:227b-42: byug pa'i rdzas su bshad pa yin //
T02TD2885E:227b-43: rus chen mnan la bdug pa bya //
T02TD2885E:227b-44: nyi ma'i 'od la mun pa bzhin //
